# Twitch clip to Discord
 This Action alows you to create a Twitch clip  ans send it as an Embed to your Discord.

## Import Code
+ Copy This Code.
```text

```

## Installation
In Streamer.bot in select `Import` from the top left.
Copy the `Import Code` and paste it into the `Import String`. 
+ Example:
+ ![Clip-To-Discord-Import](Images/Clip-To-Discord-Import.png)

+ You should now have 1 new action.
+ Example:
+ ![List-of-imported-Actions](Images/List-of-imported-Actions.png "List-of-imported-Actions")

## Example Usage
+ You can now bind this action to your StreamDeck, Deckboard action or a channel point redemption.
+ Example:
+ ![Example-Embed](Images/Example-Embed.png "Example-Embed")
